org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabUser.Query

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabUser.Query
  • Enclosing class:
    GitlabUser

    public static class GitlabUser.Query
extends java.lang.Object
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global users. Build this query with setters and call query() to execute query.

    Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/users.html#list-users

    GET /users
